body:
Can you check if it's in tensorflow_cc?

```
nm bazel-bin/tensorflow/libtensorflow_cc.so|c++filt|grep tensorflow::internal::CheckOpMessageBuilder::NewString
```

It should show as `T` (not `t`).

If you link with `-Wl,--undefined`, then `ldd` the output, what do you see?
